    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at this risk level. The hemolysis model is judged sufficiently credible to support the CPB device tolerance decision. The published literature survey provides broad corroboration of model performance across a range of centrifugal pump geometries and operating conditions that encompass the COU envelope, and aggregate RH predictions are consistent with the RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion.",
